# GeoSWMM Gateway — disk-usage alarm (per §8.3 of GatewayServerPlan.md)
#
# Every 15 minutes, check /var/lib/docker disk usage. When the "Use%"
# column exceeds 80 percent, post the offending df line to the Discord
# webhook configured in $DISCORD_WEBHOOK.
#
# Install via ops/install-disk-alarm.sh, which appends this line to
# root's crontab and tests it once.
#
# Requires:
#   - $DISCORD_WEBHOOK exported in the cron environment (or hard-coded
#     by install-disk-alarm.sh after read-from-env).
#   - curl available on the host (default on Ubuntu 24.04).
#
# At 80% usage you have ~4 GB headroom on a 20 GB disk to react.

*/15 * * * * df /var/lib/docker | awk 'NR==2 && $5+0>80 {print $0}' | curl -s -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d "@-" $DISCORD_WEBHOOK
